data.description: Welcome to this stunning newly painted 4-bedroom, 4-bathroom home nestled in the heart of Perris. With a bonus loft space that can serve as a 5th bedroom or a versatile office or home gym, this home offers flexibility and comfort for all your needs. The highlight of this home is the flexible loft space, which can be transformed into a 5th bedroom to accommodate any additional needs, serve as an office or workout from your home. This versatile area provides endless possibilities to suit your lifestyle and preferences. The expansive master suite is a true retreat and exclusively on one side of the home giving you a desirable privacy with his and hers walk in closets and spacious bathroom. This property is located near 215 freeway and you can enjoy easy access to local schools, shopping centers, ensuring a convenient and fulfilling lifestyle for you and your family.    Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this exceptional property your own! Schedule a showing today and experience the endless potential that this 4-bedroom, 4-bathroom home with a versatile loft space offers. Seller did many awesome upgrades to the home, Let's Open escrow!
